title: Schedule A Tour-Newly Renovated Apartment Homes And Luxury Amenities!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Moen Align bathroom collection in a chrome finish for a modern look', '-Engineered wood plank flooring throughout', '-Resident Portal: Enter Maintenance Requests Online when Convenient', '-The Cinema Offers Cozy Seating for Private Viewing Parties', '-Heated, Underground Garage Stalls Available with Convenient Car Washing Station', '-Whirlpool stainless steel appliance suite with French door refrigerator and backless range', '-24-Hour Fitness Center Furnished with Life Fitness Equipment', '-Large, private balcony with panoramic views', '-The Playroom with Toys and Child-Friendly Computers', '-High Intensity UVC Lamp Coupled with Bionic iWave Air Purifying Systems', '-Certified 100% sprinklered apartments', '-Dedicated Laundry Facilities with High Efficiency Equipment and Onsite Dry Cleaning', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
